(49, 1, 12, 49, 1, 13, 14, 'to the praise of his glory', 'Connection of Trust and Glory', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of trusting in Christ and the resulting praise of God''s glory. The first verse mentions those who ''first trusted in Christ,'' while the second highlights that believers are sealed ''unto the praise of his glory.''', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(49, 1, 12, 23, 12, 2, 2, 'trusted in Christ', 'Trust and Salvation Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of trust in God as a source of salvation. Ephesians highlights trusting in Christ, while Isaiah expresses trust in the Lord as salvation.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
