(49, 2, 6, 43, 17, 21, 26, 'made us sit together in heavenly places', 'Unity in Christ''s Presence', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of unity among believers in Christ. Ephesians speaks of being raised and seated together in Christ, while John highlights the desire for believers to be one as Christ is one with the Father.', 'theme', 0.489, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
