(49, 2, 7, 54, 1, 16, 17, 'exceeding riches of his grace', 'Grace and Mercy Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s grace and mercy. Both passages emphasize how God''s kindness and longsuffering are demonstrated through Christ, showcasing His attributes to believers.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(49, 2, 7, 56, 3, 4, 4, 'kindness toward us through Christ Jesus', 'Kindness of God', 'Both passages emphasize the kindness of God toward humanity. Ephesians highlights God''s kindness through Christ, while Titus speaks of the appearance of God''s kindness and love. This connection highlights a thematic continuity in the portrayal of divine kindness.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(49, 2, 7, 49, 2, 4, 4, NULL, 'God''s Richness in Mercy and Grace', 'Both passages emphasize God''s richness, with Ephesians 2:4 highlighting his ''rich mercy'' and Ephesians 2:7 focusing on the ''exceeding riches of his grace.'' This connection highlights the abundance of God''s love and kindness toward humanity.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
